HEADWORD: Porta
<hw>Por"ta</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Port⟦ae⟧</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[L., a gate. See
